-   $\left(\frac{1}{p} \sum _{j = b + 1}^p \widehat{\mu}_{x, j} \right) 
     + b \cdot c \cdot \log(\min(n, p)) / (\min(n, p))$,

-   $\log\left(\frac{1}{p} \sum _{j = b + 1}^p \widehat{\mu}_{x, j} \right)
     + b \cdot c \cdot (n + p) / (n p) \cdot \log(n p / (n + p))$,

